    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なぁなぁ、あっち見てみろよ！
すげー行列してっぞ！　あれおもしれーって、ぜってー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, hey, check that out!
That ride's line is so long! I bet it's super fun!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クールルルーーー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Coororoo!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なははは、あっちさ、見てみろ！
ぐるんぐるん、回ってるだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahahah, look over there!
It's going around and around!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>need context</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お！　すげーっ！
くぅ〜〜〜！　アレ乗ってみてーよな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa! That's amazing!
Ughhh~! I wanna try riding it!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>むはははは！　珍しく意見が合ったでねぇが。
ほれ、シェイクハンドだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mwahahah! How rare of us to come to an agreement
for once. Come, shake my hand!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごくはしゃいでるね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These two sure look happy...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと……男子はすぐテンション上がるんだから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Truly...Boys get excited easily, after all...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おーい！　ふたりとも！　いつまで休んでんだ！？
次行くぞ、次！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, how long are you guys going to keep resting?
Hurry, we're gonna leave you behind!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おっしゃー！　休憩の後は、おらのマジックハンドが、
ご機嫌なうなりをあげるぜぇい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright! After you guys have finished taking a break, it's
my turn to beat y'all into a good mood!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>could be better</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クールーーールルーーーー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cooororoo!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46888</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よっしゃーっ！　行くぜーーー！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright! Bring it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_201_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オラオラオラオラオラオラオラー！
ご機嫌だぜぇ、ベイベー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>ORA ORA ORA ORA!!
Feel better, baby!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>this is a jojo reference</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
